paragraph.paragraph:
Virtual Folder(
	../../../../images/icons/folder.ico
), in EiffelEnvision, will only be located directly under the other_project_items.xmlOther Project Items top-level folder or below another virtual folder. Virtual folder, unlike other non-top-level folders in EiffelEnvision ../project.xmlProjects, do not have an underlying disk representation. They merley represent a way to arrange project file items into a preferable hierarchy.
